					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12868840#post-4452352</guid>
				<title>AUTHOR POST OF ARCHIVAL RESURRECTION PROWESS</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12868840/scp-4367#post-4452352</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2019 03:23:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RJB_R</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1229263</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a rewrite of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-776-arc">SCP-776</a>, a magic dice which was archived for its use in the Clef-Kondraki incident tale. I've always been rather fond of the image and I'm hoping this does the work justice. Most of the reason this exists is my lovely fiancé wrote it and guided my hand through our editing process. She's really good at this.</p> <p>Also thanks to Captain Kirby, CalibriCold Rumetzen, Sebarus, Modern_Erasmus and madness_ for helping me and giving feedback during the process of writing this big boi. I believe I also received some help in IRC and don't immediately have logs for that so if I didn't credit you here just give me a solid poke in the eye.</p> <p>Image was made by far2 and has been sourced as CC <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-85952/scp-776-arc#post-4230077">here</a>.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
